<normalizedToken id="5724B44868D7EF51C609104243558174" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as wide as high in frontal view and about 1.9 
<normalizedToken id="D51832F2F147C62871F4416FF328B3CC" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as wide as long in dorsal view. POL 2.43 
<normalizedToken id="32FE881078DEFC160C6ADE5A003BF8B2" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
OOL. Malar space 0.5 
<normalizedToken id="8A19DA1EF63F7CECFC0C820F00F6E56D" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
eye height. Antennae dark brown with ventral surface of scape yellow, funicle with three long branches, with long setae. Relative measurements (length: width): scape = 33: 8; pedicel = 10: 7; F1 = 10: 6; F2 = 20: 4; F3 = 22: 4; F4 = 40: 7; clava = 40: 7. Fore wing 3.1 
<normalizedToken id="58164D4D5E6FCA3C4982A7F224F3B56D" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as wide. Hind wing about 7.1 
<normalizedToken id="7BB3C12B08DFC06FB085EDB830592D54" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as wide. MV 1.3 
<normalizedToken id="8C12865914090E6726327CFD30E40FD9" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as PMV. PMV 2.0 
<normalizedToken id="B42B515191BD1ADCDBBAFE67DA6411E4" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as STV. Metasoma almost as long as mesosoma. Petiole 1.7 
<normalizedToken id="312C9B61595D78FFCDC4E8B8C37CC583" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as wide in dorsal view. Gaster ovate, 1.9 
<normalizedToken id="EFAFD75E1D97FC1DE22B36652EEA85A0" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as wide.
</paragraph>
